		"description": "<p>Also at 14th level, whenever you enter a new settlement of at least 300 people, you can spend 8 hours visiting various businesses and gathering places to learn all of the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Who are the legitimate authorities here (mayor, local lord, king, etc.)</li>\n<li>Who is in charge of any illegitimate business here (most powerful local criminal or shady individual).</li>\n<li>Where both people can be found or how to best contact them as a stranger.</li>\n<li>Where, if anywhere, illegal goods can be purchased in this settlement.</li>\n<li>How honest, and how competent, the local law is.</li>\n</ul>",
